{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f6b2bf710f","title":"视察山东时的谈话（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"781aeb35d7","index":0,"year":1958,"month":8,"day":9,"articleId":"f6b2bf710f","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7fe419652e","type":"title","text":"视察山东时的谈话（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"75b7fc4888","type":"paragraph","text":"计划、指示不经过群众辩论，主意是你们的；辩论后，群众自已是主人了，干劲自然更足。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2a8b99541f","type":"paragraph","text":"领导必须多到下面去看，帮助基层干部总结经验，就地进行领导。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffab02f5da","type":"paragraph","text":"还是办人民公社好，它的好处是，可以把工、农、商、学、兵合在一起，便于领导。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9df235abc4","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的小米长得不好嘛，我看群众的干劲太少！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"020fbc4576","type":"paragraph","text":"好，你这个人（历城县北园乡北园农业社主任李书成）不干就不干，一干就大干的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"197b867f1d","type":"paragraph","text":"你好，你（山东省农科所副所长秦杰）学的学问能用上了。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dca17a9948","type":"paragraph","text":"是应该压追你们一下，不压追，你们就不会上梁山。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62c1dc01dd","type":"paragraph","text":"你们研究一下棉花为什么落桃，棉花落桃的问题，是否可以研究个办法，叫它少落或不落。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47c961e756","type":"paragraph","text":"你们行还是农民行","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45e8d3dfb1","type":"paragraph","text":"那很好，你们要继续努力，力争上游。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa1391e388","type":"paragraph","text":"你们十得很好，都鼓足了干劲","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":520,"end":520}},"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"333961393a","type":"title","text":"视察山东时的谈话（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4cfe11d772","type":"paragraph","text":"你好，你（指山东省农科所付所长秦杰）学的学问能用上了。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"613384dc12","type":"paragraph","text":"领导必须多到下面去看，帮助基层干部总结经验，就地进行领导。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a99cec888","type":"paragraph","text":"你们行还是农民行？","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8cc13678d0","type":"paragraph","text":"你们研究一下（棉花）为什么落桃，（棉花落桃）的问题，是否可以研究个办法，叫它少落或不落。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d6f6d09ad1","type":"paragraph","text":"（在接见山东著名的劳动模范，农业社的干部们时说）你们干得很好，都鼓足了干劲。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9890a8b4a","type":"paragraph","text":"那很好，你们要继续努力，力争上游。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ecbe5350eb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席特别强调布置各项工作必通过群众鸣放辩论，他说：计划、指示不经过群众辩论，主意是你们的；辩论后，群众自己是主人了，干劲自然更足。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f25f0fcf7f","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的小米长得不好嘛，我看群众的干劲太少！","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f45e5e8e75","type":"paragraph","text":"还是办人民公社好，它的好处是，可以把工、农，商、学、兵合在一起，便于领导。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f85ee9ae4b","type":"paragraph","text":"是应该压迫你们一下，不压迫，你们就不会上梁山。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f88c6ea7ae","type":"paragraph","text":"好，你这个人（指历城县北园乡北园农业社主任李书成。）不干就不干，一干就大干的。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"f6b2bf710f","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":199,"end":198}}}},"__N_SSG":true}